#: ../src/guide/views/view.md
msgid "In Yii3 views are typically PHP files that contain presentation logic and HTML markup. The view system provides a flexible way to organize your presentation layer and supports features like layouts and partial views. Instead of using plain PHP templates, you can leverage [one of the template engines such as Twig](template-engines.md)."
